DIGEST
SB 133 Reengrossed 2026 Regular Session Cloud
Present law provides for vehicles left unattended on state highway shoulders. Proposed law
removes the provision of "unattended".
Present law provides the Department of Transportation and Development (DOTD) is the
agency with jurisdiction over autonomous commercial motor vehicles and automated driving
